### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
### PoTagGame — HTTP scratch file
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000  (HTTP profile)
###          https://localhost:5001  (HTTPS profile)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### ── Health ──────────────────────────────────────
# Expected: 200 OK  {"status":"Healthy"}
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### ── Diagnostics ──────────────────────────────────
# Expected: 200 OK  JSON with app/env/server/connections keys
GET {{baseUrl}}/diag
Accept: application/json

###

### ── OpenAPI document ──────────────────────────────
# (Available once Scalar/OpenAPI is wired in Program.cs)
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

###

### ── SignalR negotiate (verify hub routing) ────────
# Expected: 302 / 200 JSON with connectionId + availableTransports
POST {{baseUrl}}/tagHub/negotiate?negotiateVersion=1
Content-Type: application/json

###
